      "review_summary": "The PR adds an OpenAI Responses create-plus-drain retry for streamed encrypted-content failures, broadens encrypted-content error detection and sanitization, and adds focused stream retry tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +179, Tests +404. Total +583 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level: current main and v2026.6.9 only retry create() failures, while processResponsesStream throws streamed response.failed/type:error failures outside that retry path; the linked issue provides current-release provider failure evidence. I did not run a live Copilot session because it requires private credentials and affected history.",
